        <div class="icon-wrap"><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg></div>
        <h3 data-i18n="f2_t">Tactical Speed</h3>
        <p data-i18n="f2_d">Our optimized stealth protocol delivers blazing speeds — stream, game, and browse without lag.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card glass">
        <div class="icon-wrap"><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg></div>
        <h3 data-i18n="f3_t">Global Network</h3>
        <p data-i18n="f3_d">Connect to 5,500+ servers in 90+ countries. Access restricted content from anywhere in the world.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card glass">
        <div class="icon-wrap"><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.94 17.94A10.07 10.07 0 0 1 12 20c-7 0-11-8-11-8a18.45 18.45 0 0 1 5.06-5.94M9.9 4.24A9.12 9.12 0 0 1 12 4c7 0 11 8 11 8a18.5 18.5 0 0 1-2.16 3.19m-6.72-1.07a3 3 0 1 1-4.24-4.24"/><line x1="1" y1="1" x2="23" y2="23"/></svg></div>
        <h3 data-i18n="f4_t">Strict No-Logs</h3>
        <p data-i18n="f4_d">We never track, store, or share your browsing activity. Your privacy is 100% absolute and guaranteed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card glass">
        <div class="icon-wrap"><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12.55a11 11 0 0 1 14.08 0"/><path d="M1.42 9a16 16 0 0 1 21.16 0"/><path d="M8.53 16.11a6 6 0 0 1 6.95 0"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12.01" y2="20"/></svg></div>
        <h3 data-i18n="f5_t">Public Wi-Fi Shield</h3>
        <p data-i18n="f5_d">Stay safe on coffee shop, airport, and hotel networks with automatic cyber-threat protection.</p>
